\c 39
\s Inkosi yeBhabhiloni ithuma izithunywa kuHezekhiya
\p
\v 1 Ngalesosikhathi uMerodaki-Baladani, indodana kaBaladani inkosi yeBhabhiloni\x + 39.8. 2 Kho. 20.12-19.\x*, wathumela izincwadi lesipho kuHezekhiya, ngoba wayezwile ukuthi ubekade egula, useqinile.
\v 2 UHezekhiya wasethokoza ngazo, wabatshengisa indlu yokuligugu kwakhe, isiliva\x + 33.1,23. 2 Kho. 18.15,16.\x*, legolide, lamakha\x + 57.9.\x*, lamafutha amahle\x + 57.9.\x*, lendlu yonke yezikhali zakhe, lakho konke okwatholakala kokuligugu kwakhe\x + 33.1,23. 2 Kho. 18.15,16.\x*; kakubanga lalutho endlini yakhe lembusweni wakhe wonke uHezekhiya angabatshengisanga lona.
\p
\v 3 Wasefika uIsaya umprofethi enkosini uHezekhiya, wathi kuyo: Atheni lamadoda? Futhi avele ngaphi esiza kuwe? UHezekhiya wasesithi: Avele elizweni elikhatshana esiza kimi, eBhabhiloni\x + 5.26.\x*.
\v 4 Wasesithi: Aboneni endlini yakho? UHezekhiya wasesithi: Abone konke okusendlini yami; kakulalutho phakathi kokuligugu kwami engingawatshengisanga lona.
\v 5 UIsaya wasesithi kuHezekhiya: Zwana ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla.
\v 6 Khangela, insuku ziyeza lapho konke okusendlini yakho, lalokho oyihlo abakubuthelelayo kuze kube lamuhla, kuzathwalelwa eBhabhiloni; kakuyikusala lutho, kutsho iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 7 Njalo bazathatha emadodaneni akho azaphuma kuwe, ozawazala; njalo abe ngabathenwa esigodlweni senkosi yeBhabhiloni\x + 13.22.\x*.
\v 8 UHezekhiya wasesithi kuIsaya: Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* olikhulumileyo lilungile. Wathi futhi: Ngoba kuzakuba lokuthula leqiniso ensukwini zami.
